name: DOS "FOMOCHROME" PUNK
description:
DOS FOMOCHROME PUNK Split between Blockchain worlds. Born from 2-tone color wheels and 3D renders. 

This is a historical moment for the community. When worlds merge something magical manifests... 

Not affiliated with Larva Labs or Max Capacity. Made with permission from Max Capacity Free Drop only available to holders of Max Capacity's DOS Punks, Pak's Fomo & BitSavage FractalVerse! 

DOS Punks is a collection of 1000 artworks by Max Capacity, half on the Tezos blockchain and half on the Ethereum blockchain. Each one is made with a DOS character set and various retro-gaming/computing color palettes.
